{
  "total_duration": 673.777,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 12.496,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你有没有遇到过一种声音，白天也有，晚上也有，久了以后真的会让人受不了？今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Mad or not?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“是不是疯了”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 12.846,
      "end": 26.157,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "mad"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是严肃的医学诊断，而是日常夸张。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The noise is driving me mad"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，意思是“这个噪音快把我烦坏了，快让我受不了了”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 26.507,
      "end": 38.987,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课也不是讲“飞机很可怕”。真正的故事是：一个机场启用了，飞机日夜飞过，邻居陆续搬走，主人公拿到一大笔搬走的钱，可他还是决定留下。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 39.337,
      "end": 52.657,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先把旧场景接到现在。机场、铁路、高架桥、地铁工地、商场、体育场，这些设施对城市可能很有用，但如果刚好建在你家旁边，生活就会被改变。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 53.007,
      "end": 67.823,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "aeroplane"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是英式英语，更常见的现代说法是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "airplane or plane"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "came into use"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思是开始使用、开始运营。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 68.172,
      "end": 77.492,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以今天抓住这条链："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "airport built, came into use, noise night and day, neighbours driven away, money offered, determined to stay"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 77.842,
      "end": 85.442,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一帧，主人公住在机场附近的一座老房子里。飞机从上空经过，白天听得到，晚上也听得到。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 85.792,
      "end": 97.848,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文一开头说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Aeroplanes are slowly driving me mad."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "slowly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很重要，不是突然崩溃，而是每天一点点被噪音折磨。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 98.198,
      "end": 114.393,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接着他说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I live near an airport and passing planes can be heard night and day."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "night and day"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是日夜不停。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "can be heard"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是被动语态，重点是“这种声音到处都能被听见”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 114.743,
      "end": 120.463,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二帧，机场本来很多年前就建好了，但一开始没有真正启用。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 120.813,
      "end": 132.473,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The airport was built years ago, but for some reason it could not be used then."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "for some reason"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是由于某种原因，课文没有展开解释。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 132.823,
      "end": 145.79,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后转折来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Last year, however, it came into use."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "came into use"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是开始使用、开始运营。从那以后，附近人的生活才真正被改变。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 146.14,
      "end": 155.14,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三帧，噪音开始把人推走。不是房子都倒了，而是生活太吵，很多人受不了，只好离开。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 155.49,
      "end": 161.134,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Over a hundred people must have been driven away from their homes by the noise."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 161.484,
      "end": 175.692,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must have been driven away"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一个很关键的组合。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must have"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示“我几乎可以肯定已经发生了”，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "been driven away"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是被动：他们是被噪音逼走的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 176.041,
      "end": 182.201,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "主人公说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am one of the few people left."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他成了少数还留下来的人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 182.551,
      "end": 190.247,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四帧，压力又升级了。主人公有时甚至想："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "this house will be knocked down by a passing plane"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 190.597,
      "end": 199.917,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这是一种夸张想象，不要把画面做成飞机撞房子。它是在表达：飞机从上空经过时，他觉得房子都快受不了了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 200.267,
      "end": 213.05,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "后面还有一个现实压力："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I have been offered a large sum of money to go away."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a large sum of money"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一大笔钱，这里像是为了让他搬走而给出的补偿。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 213.4,
      "end": 229.544,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可他说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am determined to stay here."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "determined"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是坚定的，已经下定决心的。别人说他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must be mad"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，他最后也半开玩笑地承认："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "they are probably right"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 229.894,
      "end": 240.617,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇课文最容易误会四个地方："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "mad"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "aeroplane"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "came into use"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，还有那一大笔钱到底是什么意思。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 240.967,
      "end": 244.409,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "mad"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是真的疯了吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 244.759,
      "end": 258.271,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这篇里不是。它是生活里的夸张说法。比如噪音太大、作业太多、同一首歌一直循环，你可能说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It is driving me mad."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "意思是“快把我烦坏了”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 258.621,
      "end": 261.507,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "aeroplane"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 261.857,
      "end": 275.184,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "aeroplane"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是英式英语里的飞机。现在很多学生更熟的是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "airplane or plane"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。课文比较老，所以保留了"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "aeroplane"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个词。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 275.534,
      "end": 280.049,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "机场不是很多年前就建好了吗，为什么去年才影响他？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 280.398,
      "end": 297.174,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为建好不等于启用。课文说机场"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "was built years ago"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，但当时"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "could not be used"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。到了去年，它"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "came into use"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也就是开始运营，飞机才真的日夜飞过。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 297.524,
      "end": 301.17,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那别人给他钱，是不是他已经同意搬走了？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 301.52,
      "end": 317.092,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I have been offered a large sum of money"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "只是说“有人向我提供了一大笔钱”。这像是补偿或搬走的条件，但他没有接受。下一句马上说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am determined to stay here."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 317.442,
      "end": 320.882,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么大家说他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must be mad"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 321.232,
      "end": 331.512,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为邻居都走了，噪音又日夜不停，还有钱可以拿，他却还是要留下。这个选择看起来不合理，但对他来说，这里是他的家。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 331.862,
      "end": 334.862,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Aeroplanes are slowly driving me mad."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 335.211,
      "end": 339.315,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I live near an airport and passing planes can be heard night and day."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 339.665,
      "end": 344.633,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The airport was built years ago, but for some reason it could not be used then."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 344.983,
      "end": 348.319,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Last year, however, it came into use."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 348.669,
      "end": 353.397,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Over a hundred people must have been driven away from their homes by the noise."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 353.747,
      "end": 356.411,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am one of the few people left."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 356.761,
      "end": 360.985,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Sometimes I think this house will be knocked down by a passing plane."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 361.335,
      "end": 366.639,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I have been offered a large sum of money to go away, but I am determined to stay here."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 366.989,
      "end": 370.853,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Everybody says I must be mad and they are probably right."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 371.202,
      "end": 373.794,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "mad"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "mad"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 374.144,
      "end": 375.656,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "mad"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "mad"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
