          "lang": "en",
          "text": "determined"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是坚定的、下定决心的。它常和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "to"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "连在一起："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "determined to stay"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，坚定地留下；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "determined to finish"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，坚定地完成。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 454.365,
      "end": 463.917,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "determined"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "主人公说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I am determined to stay here."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "噪音、邻居搬走、钱的提议都没有改变他的决定。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 54,
      "start": 464.267,
      "end": 472.938,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "determined"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个词带出结尾的喜剧感：别人说他肯定是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "mad"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，可他就是很"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "determined"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 55,
      "start": 473.288,
      "end": 481.8,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "grammar"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是被动语态，但不要先背公式。先看主人公为什么总是在“被影响”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 56,
      "start": 482.15,
      "end": 492.038,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "飞机从头顶经过，声音"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "can be heard night and day"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。重点不是谁在听，而是这种声音到处都能被听到。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 57,
      "start": 492.388,
      "end": 503.843,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "机场"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "was built years ago"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，但当时"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "could not be used"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。重点是机场这个东西经历了“被建好”和“不能被使用”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 58,
      "start": 504.193,
      "end": 518.865,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "邻居"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must have been driven away by the noise"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这句话里，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "must have"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是对过去的强烈推测，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "been driven away"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是被动，说明他们是被噪音逼走的。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 59,
      "start": 519.215,
      "end": 529.71,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "房子在主人公想象里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will be knocked down by a passing plane"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这不是事故报道，而是他被噪音压得太久后的夸张感觉。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 60,
      "start": 530.06,
      "end": 540.212,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后，他自己"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "has been offered a large sum of money"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。他不是主动去要钱，而是别人向他提出了这个搬走的条件。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 61,
      "start": 540.562,
      "end": 551.002,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以这样理解：主动力量在外面，机场、飞机、噪音、出钱的人都在推他；被动语态把镜头放在被影响的人和东西上。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 62,
      "start": 551.352,
      "end": 561.152,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这篇的被动不是为了复杂，而是为了讲清楚一件事："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "outside forces are changing his home, but he is determined to stay"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 63,
      "start": 561.502,
      "end": 576.142,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好，把今天的故事放进自己的生活。你不一定要写机场，可以写外面的施工声、楼上的脚步声、反复出现的作业、练习、排队，或者一个让你很烦但你还想坚持的项目。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 64,
      "start": 576.492,
      "end": 590.531,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的小框架是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The ___ is driving me mad. I have been offered ___. But I am determined to ___."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 65,
      "start": 590.881,
      "end": 600.941,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比如："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The construction noise is driving me mad. I have been offered a quieter room. But I am determined to finish my homework."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 66,
      "start": 601.291,
      "end": 607.339,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "也可以轻一点："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "This homework is driving me mad, but I am determined to finish it."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
